{"analytics_identifier":"PC386","base_path":"/government/organisations/channel-4","content_id":"2766247d-5731-46f7-9dfe-fc74f243929d","description":"Channel 4 (C4) is public service broadcaster and works across television, film and digital media. In addition to the main Channel 4 service, its portfolio includes E4, More4, Film4 and 4Music, as well as online activities that includes channel4.com, Channel 4’s bespoke video-on-demand service 4oD and standalone digital projects. C4 is a public corporation of the Department for Culture, Media and Sport .","details":{"acronym":"C4","alternative_format_contact_email":"","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>Channel 4 (C4) is public service broadcaster and works across television, film and digital media. In addition to the main Channel 4 service, its portfolio includes E4, More4, Film4 and 4Music, as well as online activities that includes channel4.com, Channel 4’s bespoke video-on-demand service 4oD and standalone digital projects.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Channel 4\">C4</abbr> is a public corporation of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/department-for-culture-media-and-sport\">Department for Culture, Media and Sport</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"department-for-culture-media-sport","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"no-identity","formatted_title":"Channel 4"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[],"ordered_featured_links":[],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"exempt","updated_at":null,"url":"http://www.channel4.com"},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"public_corporation","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2012-11-12T12:12:52+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"PC386","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/channel-4","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/a